{"tid":1304731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個啲咩話要集中五大訴求，唔好搞其他，九成係鬼","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T00:09:56.000Z","uid":20414,"like":11,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5538b64a79dfdef222820dfa1a49e418a5bc9b","tid":1304731,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"今日一窩風出 post, 唔係鬼就假<br />\n建制派最好你地個個都係晒金鍾坐係度<br />\n有咩實際作用？<br />\n<br />\n家下篇地開花個個士氣高脹，一野搞死佢成個利益集團，佢都唔知應付邊個好<br />\n<br />\n屌那星話左各有各做架嗎，個個都冇忘記五大訴求，一有事就出番晒黎架啦<br />\n<br />\n個個 post 都正評個啲用腦諗下先啦，個啲失敗主義先係一四年失敗原因呀"},{"pid":"94d2e95ec71e21b5cdac6c3f569e57fde022ecf1","tid":1304731,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"推番"},{"pid":"21566b2b96f9130b9e41c8ff77028c1673723b5e","tid":1304731,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"個人認為太多「失敗論」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af211227fab0adb8ea4464f2d0cd3ea285b8b602","tid":1304731,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"個咩亞倫哥 P 牌仔"},{"pid":"ab8c1535478e2a3a466ad6d2f1e181d3c9613180","tid":1304731,"uid":58841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"睇清楚話要五大訴求個班個乜<br />\n佢地叫你只貼不守<br />\n唔係死攬"},{"pid":"b3a8f37491b3349cd6cc31292a5846733ca405de","tid":1304731,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇清楚話要五大訴求個班<span style=\"color: red;\">講</span>乜<br />\n佢地叫你只貼不守<br />\n唔係死攬</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd554483ee3d7f55c3f904ab3ce6f781461740fa","tid":1304731,"uid":34478,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"又話拆一貼十<br />\n屌你咪由得佢拆<br />\n守嚟托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼完做其他宣